description:
We are mental, physical, and spiritual beings. God wants us to prosper in all dimensions, yet many of us struggle with mental health issues. Dan Gabbert looks at Jesus method of dealing with mental and spiritual challenges. What are the ways in which Jesus heals mental and spiritual problems?

Because He created us, Jesus knows how to help us in our struggles. Gods way of healing a broken heart is based on the principles of His Word and has been validated scientifically and by the Spirit of Prophecy. Jesus is the answer to our spiritual and mental health problems.

Find out how Jesus heals emotional and spiritual affliction. Learn about Biblical Response Therapy.


Watch more: https://adtv.watch/

Subscribe to our YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/OfficialADTVChannel?sub_confirmation=1
